            "text": "<p></p><p><strong>Dear fellow sufferer,</strong><br/><br/>Let's be honest.<br/><br/>There is nothing <strong>\"mild\"</strong> about a headache.<br/><br/>Whether it's the crushing pressure wrapping around your skull until you can't form a single thought  or the blinding, pulsating force of a Migraine that drives you into a dark room and locks the door, the pain is real. </p><p><strong>And it is stealing your life.</strong><br/><br/>Here is something the <strong>pharmaceutical companies </strong>would rather you never found out:</p>",
