            "text": "<p>The <strong>\"biological secret\"</strong> locked inside your skull<br/><br/>Tom Collins founded Duracalm after uncovering a fatal flaw in how head pain gets treated: <strong>the hardware gets addressed, but the software gets ignored.</strong><br/><br/>Here's what's actually happening inside your skull when you have an episode.<br/><br/>A headache isn't just a physical knot. <strong>It is a neurological loop.</strong><br/><br/>If you have Migraines: <strong>Your nervous system is stuck</strong> in \"high alert,\" typically involving the trigeminal nerve and vascular inflammation.</p><p><br/>If you have Tension Headaches: <strong>Your neck muscles are weak and shortening due to posture</strong>, constantly pulling on the base of your skull.<br/><br/><strong>A pill cannot fix a software problem. </strong></p><p>Your system needs to be reprogrammed.<br/></p>",
